ound%20targets%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20Hamas.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EIsrael%20Defence%20spokesperson%20Daniel%20Hagari%20said%20that%20the%20troops%20were%20%26quot%3Bstill%20in%20the%20field%26quot%3B%20and%20claimed%20that%20they%20were%20fighting%20a%20weaker%20enemy.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20aid%20trucks%2C%20carrying%20food%20and%20water%2C%20will%20be%20allowed%20into%20Gaza%20today.%20Not%20only%20has%20the%20region%20been%20hit%20by%20the%20Israeli%20strikes%2C%20they%20are%20also%20facing%20severe%20shortages%20of%20food%2C%20fuel%2C%20and%20medicines.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EInternet%20and%20phone%20services%20were%20also%20cut%20off%20amid%20the%20overnight%20strikes%20on%20Friday.%20Human%20Rights%20Watch%2C%20an%20NGO%2C%20has%20expressed%20concern%20that%20a%20communication%20blackout%20risks%20providing%20cover%20for%20mass%20atrocities.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EA%20thick%20haze%20of%20smoke%20covered%20Gaza%20and%20southern%20Israel%20after%20the%20night%20of%20heavy%20bombardment%2C%20according%20to%20journalists%20covering%20the%20war.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EA%20BBC%20journalist%20described%20%26quot%3Btotal%20chaos%26quot%3B%20during%20the%20night%20of%20strikes%20and%20in%20its%20aftermath.%20%26quot%3BThere%20was%20a%20huge%20bombardment%20in%20the%20north%20of%20Gaza%20Strip%20on%20a%20scale%20we've%20never%20seen%20before.%20At%20the%20hospital%20here%2C%20ambulance%20drivers%20told%20me%20they%20couldn't%20communicate%20with%20anyone%2C%20so%20they%20were%20just%20driving%20in%20the%20direction%20of%20the%20explosions%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Rushdi%20Abualouf.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EHamas%20has%20said%20that%20its%20operatives%20are%20ready%20to%20confront%20Israeli%20attacks%20with%20%26quot%3Bfull%20force%26quot%3B%20in%20Gaza.%20The%20Palestinian%20militant%20group%20that%20rules%20Gaza%20had%20said%20its%20operatives%20were%20clashing%20with%20Israeli%20troops%20in%20areas%20near%20the%20border%20with%20Israel.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3