ic%20Industrial%20Policy%20Help%20Integration%20With%20Global%20Value%20Chain%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F28143150%2Fpexels-andrey-matveev-4211136.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIndustrial%20policy%2C%20the%20idea%20that%20the%20government%20can%20play%20a%20significant%20role%20in%20building%20out%20parts%20of%20the%20economy%20for%20various%20purposes%2C%20is%20back%20globally.%20The%20United%20States%20Inflation%20Reduction%20Act%20is%20the%20prime%20example%2C%20using%20state%20subsidies%2C%20tax%20breaks%2C%20loans%2C%20and%20grants%20to%20support%20industries%20that%20the%20US%20has%20deemed%20strategic.%20India%2C%20too%2C%20is%20no%20stranger%20to%20this%20trend.%20India%20introduced%20Production%20Linked%20Incentives%20in%202020%2C%20providing%20a%20financial%20boost%20to%20firms%20that%20expanded%20their%20manufacturing%20within%20the%20country%2C%20starting%20with%20three%20industries%20%E2%80%93%20pharmaceutical%2C%20electronics%2C%20and%20medical%20devices%20%E2%80%93%20and%20then%20expanding%20them%20to%20cover%20many%20more%20sectors.%20%3Cb%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20how%20do%20these%20domestic-focused%20policies%20fit%20into%20broader%20efforts%20to%20integrate%20into%20the%20%E2%80%9Cglobal%20value%20chain%E2%80%9D%20and%20the%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fpolitics%2Fminister-jaishankar-bats-for-re-globalisation-at-b20-summit-11693125052729.html%5C%22%3Ediversified%2C%20democratic%E2%80%9D%20re-globalisation%20that%20India%20has%20called%20for%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20understand%2C%20we%20have%20to%20go%20back%20to%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20and%20the%20discourse%20around%20the%20global%20value%20chain%20that%20emerged%20at%20the%20time.%20The%20ripple%20effects%20of%20disruptions%20caused%20by%20the%20pandemic%20brought%20home%20the%20characteristics%20of%20a%20globalised%20world%20that%20obtains%20many%20items%20of%20consumption%20through%20the%20global%20value%20chain.%20The%20important%20question%20then%20turned%20to%20the%20risks%20associated%20with%20these%20chains%20and%20their%20resilience.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUntil%20recently%2C%20countries%20were%20trying%20to%20integrate%20into%20existing%20global%20value%20chains.%20Global%20value%20chain%20participation%20generally%20brings%20economic%20benefits%20in%20terms%20of%20enhanced%20productivity%20as%20well%20as%20greater%20sophistication%20and%20diversification%20of%20exports.%20Consequently%2C%20understanding%20what%20determines%20participation%20in%20global%20value%20chains%20has%20implications%20for%20policymaking.%20Yet%20the%20gains%20from%20value%20chain%20participation%20vary%20significantly%20between%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETypically%2C%20integration%20in%20global%20value%20chains%20is%20captured%20through%20backward%20and%20forward%20linkages.%20Backward%20linkages%20measure%20how%20an%20economy%20imports%20intermediate%20goods%20or%20services%20as%20inputs%20in%20the%20production%20of%20its%20own%20exports%2C%20while%20forward%20linkages%20refer%20to%20inputs%20provided%20by%20one%20country%20to%20another%2C%20which%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20produces%20consumer%20goods%20that%20are%20further%20exported%20to%20third%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20times%2C%20many%20countries%20have%20resorted%20to%20industrial%20policy%20to%20decouple%20from%20over-reliance%20on%20certain%20trading%20partners.%20But%20how%20do%20we%20make%20sense%20of%20these%20production%20networks%20in%20the%20context%20of%20India%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EIntegration%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGlobal%20value%20chains%20are%20networked%20through%20lead%20firms%2C%20usually%20major%20multinational%20companies%20that%20play%20key%20roles%20in%20building%20these%20value%20chains.%20From%20a%20country%E2%80%99s%20point%20of%20view%2C%20belonging%20to%20these%20chains%20leads%20to%20networks%20and%20exports.%20Global%20value%20chain%20participation%20is%20dependent%20on%20a%20variety%20of%20factors%2C%20including%20the%20size%20and%20location%20of%20a%20country%2C%20its%20manufacturing%20share%20in%20GDP%2C%20and%20trade%20and%20investment%20policies.%20A%20country%E2%80%99s%20global%20value%20chain%20integration%20matters%20due%20to%20the%20nature%20of%20trade%2C%20which%2C%20since%20the%20mid-1960s%2C%20has%20increasingly%20been%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fabs%2Fpii%2FS002219961100122X%5C%22%3Eintermediate%20goods%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20the%20inputs%20that%20are%20used%20in%20the%20production%20process%20that%20lead%20to%20final%20consumer%20goods.%20Certain%20factors%20like%20lowering%20transport%20costs%2C%20easing%20tariffs%2C%20and%20technological%20advancements%20in%20transport%20have%20led%20to%20an%20increase%20in%20trade%20in%20intermediates%20whereby%20value%20is%20added%20in%20each%20subsequent%20stage%20in%20factories%20located%20in%20different%20countries.%20This%20has%20led%20to%20regions%20or%20countries%20producing%20and%20specialising%20in%20certain%20goods%20and%20the%20moniker%20of%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fonlinelibrary.wiley.com%2Fdoi%2Fabs%2F10.1111%2Ftwec.12189%5C%22%3EFactory%20Asia%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20for%20electronic%20products.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20not%20belonging%20to%20these%20chains%20means%20it%20is%20difficult%20for%20countries%20to%20break%20into%20export%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F28143351%2FElectronics_factory_in_Shenzhen.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F28143351%2FElectronics_factory_in_Shenzhen.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F28143351%2FElectronics_factory_in_Shenzhen-300x165.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682243%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22562%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERepresentative%20image%20of%20an%20electronics%20factory%20in%20Shenzhen.%20Photo%3A%20Steve%20Jurvetson%2FWikimedia%20Commons%2C%20CC%20BY%202.0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ELead%20firms%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20these%2C%20the%20role%20of%20lead%20firms%20is%20important.%20Lead%20firms%20have%20been%20defined%20as%20small%2C%20medium%2C%20or%20large%20firms%20that%20have%20forward%20or%20backward%20linkages%20with%20a%20large%20number%20of%20micro%2C%20small%2C%20and%20medium%20enterprises%20(MSMEs).%20A%20lead%20firm%20governs%20the%20whole%20of%20a%20value%20chain.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20emergence%20of%20lead%20firms%20and%20global%20value%20chain%20participation%20depends%20on%20factors%20that%20lead%20to%20a%20conducive%20business%20environment%2C%20attracting%20foreign%20investment%2C%20and%20internationalisation%20of%20domestic%20firms.%20Internationalisation%20of%20domestic%20firms%20can%20be%20done%20when%20they%20start%20exporting%20to%20international%20buyers%20and%20through%20imports%20of%20intermediates%20by%20domestic%20final%20producers.%20Global%20value%20chains%20in%20manufacturing%20can%20better%20contribute%20to%20employment%20creation%2C%20skills%20upgrading%2C%20and%20other%20benefits%20associated%20with%20manufacturing-led%20industrialisation.%20Across%20this%20ecosystem%2C%20there%20is%20a%20desire%20to%20create%20an%20environment%20that%20supports%20local%20manufacturers%20as%20they%20attempt%20to%20upgrade%20their%20productive%20capabilities%20and%20increase%20their%20competitiveness.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20many%20domestic%20firms%20in%20developing%20countries%2C%20especially%20MSMEs%2C%20do%20not%20integrate%20into%20global%20value%20chains%20easily%2C%20and%20face%20challenges%20in%20global%20value%20chain%20participation.%20The%20rise%20in%20South-South%20trade%20has%20made%20local%20and%20regional%20value%20chains%20more%20important%20for%20developing%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20global%20value%20chain%20literature%20stresses%20the%20role%20lead%20firms%20(such%20as%20global%20buyers)%20play%20in%20supporting%20producers%E2%80%99%20learning%20and%20innovation%20activities%20in%20less%20developed%20countries%20by%20transferring%20knowledge%20to%20their%20suppliers.%20However%2C%20it%20has%20been%20noted%20that%20while%20these%20firms%20generally%20outsource%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.researchgate.net%2Fpublication%2F42791981_A_Handbook_for_Value_Chain_Research%5C%22%3Ecommodity-like%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20activities%20that%20add%20little%20value%2C%20they%20retain%20direct%20control%20over%20intangible%2C%20high%20value-added%20activities%20as%20opposed%20to%20low%20value-added%20activities.%20Hence%2C%20the%20transfer%20of%20knowledge%20occurs%20more%20through%20certain%20activities%20or%20tasks%20and%20certain%20industries.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20upgrading%20to%20high%20value-added%20activities%20can%20raise%20domestic%20labour%20productivity%20and%20skills%2C%20developing%20countries%20are%20often%20locked%20in%20low%20value-added%20activities%20with%20little%20or%20no%20technology%20transfer.%20Upgrading%20is%20defined%20as%20%E2%80%9Cstrategies%20that%20firms%2C%20countries%2C%20or%20regions%20implement%20to%20move%20toward%20higher%20value-added%20activities%20and%20increased%20value%20capture.%E2%80%9D%20The%20role%20of%20leading%20firms%20becomes%20critical%20in%20this%20context.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFrom%20a%20policy%20perspective%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fopenknowledge.worldbank.org%2Fbitstreams%2F34999319-7d14-5033-8dd0-31225100cf68%2Fdownload%5C%22%3Ehow%20global%20value%20chains%20integrate%20into%20the%20economy%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20critical%20and%20the%20role%20of%20the%20lead%20firm%20is%20vital.%20Also%2C%20the%20role%20of%20industrial%20and%20other%20policies%20in%20encouraging%20global%20value%20chain%20integration%20and%20upgrading%20is%20significant.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWhither%20industrial%20policy%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndustrial%20policy%20is%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20development%20policy%20and%20has%20often%20taken%20various%20names%20(e.g.%2C%20export%20facilitation%2C%20promotion%20of%20foreign%20investment%2C%20or%20free%20trade%20zones).%20It%20is%20not%20only%20about%20incentives%20given%20to%20manufacturing%20industries%20but%20also%20those%20given%20to%20services%20or%20agriculture.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETheoretically%2C%20the%20argument%20for%20industrial%20policy%20stems%20from%20market%20failure.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdrodrik.scholar.harvard.edu%2Ffiles%2Fdani-rodrik%2Ffiles%2Fgreen_industrial_policy.pdf%5C%22%3EEconomist%20Dani%20Rodrik%20argues%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20need%20for%20industrial%20policy%20is%20theoretically%20sound%20and%20well-articulated.%20It%20can%20address%20market%20failures%2C%20but%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20implement%20in%20practice.%20As%20he%20explains%2C%20the%20conventional%20case%20for%20industrial%20policy%20is%20due%20to%20market%20failures%20in%20markets%20for%20credit%2C%20labour%2C%20products%2C%20or%20knowledge.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20two%20main%20objections%20to%20industrial%20policy%20in%20practice%2C%20according%20to%20Rodrik.%20One%20is%20information%20asymmetry%20and%20the%20other%20is%20corruption%20and%20rent-seeking.%20In%20the%20first%20case%2C%20it%20is%20impossible%20for%20governments%20to%20identify%20winners%20in%20firms%2C%20sectors%2C%20or%20markets%20that%20are%20impacted%20by%20imperfect%20markets%20%E2%80%93%20yet%20industrial%20policy%2C%20in%20some%20ways%2C%20forces%20them%20to.%20Secondly%2C%20it%20is%20argued%20that%20industrial%20policy%20often%20leads%20to%20corruption%20or%20rent-seeking.%20There%20are%20arguments%20on%20the%20empirical%20evaluation%20of%20industrial%20policy%20by%20both%20the%20proponents%20and%20opponents%20of%20industrial%20policy.%20Proponents%20suggest%20that%20in%20many%20instances%2C%20usually%20backed%20by%20case-based%20evidence%2C%20industrial%20policy%20works.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20integration%20and%20industrial%20policy%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDespite%20India%E2%80%99s%20manufacturing%20prowess%2C%20especially%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tandfonline.com%2Fdoi%2Fabs%2F10.1080%2F09692290.2012.756414%5C%22%3Emedium-tech%20industries%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20its%20participation%20in%20global%20value%20chains%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.routledge.com%2FGlobal-Value-Chains-and-the-Missing-Links-Cases-from-Indian-Industry%2FRay-Miglani%2Fp%2Fbook%2F9780367734503%5C%22%3Eremains%20limited%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Moreover%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20participation%20in%20global%20value%20chains%20is%20largely%20concentrated%20in%20a%20few%20industries%20(e.g.%20automobiles).%20India%20has%20also%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjournals.sagepub.com%2Fdoi%2Fabs%2F10.1177%2F00157325211073848%5C%22%3Elosing%20its%20share%20of%20exports%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20labour-intensive%20products%2C%20especially%20garments.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20in%20the%20case%20of%20India%2C%20while%20product%20upgrading%20(defined%20as%20the%20movement%20into%20higher%20value-added%20products%20within%20a%20global%20value%20chain)%20and%20process%20upgrading%20(which%20involves%20increased%20productivity%20in%20existing%20activities%20within%20a%20global%20value%20chain)%20have%20occurred%2C%20functional%20upgrading%20(which%20involves%20the%20movement%20into%20more%20technologically%20sophisticated%20or%20more%20integrated%20aspects%20of%20a%20production%20process)%20and%20intersectoral%20upgrading%20has%20been%20limited.%20This%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.adb.org%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fpublication%2F183908%2Fsawp-043.pdf%5C%22%3Ebeen%20the%20case%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20garments.%20Inter-sectoral%20or%20chain%20upgrading%20involves%20a%20move%20into%20higher%20value-added%20supply%20chains.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDeveloping%20countries%20can%20better%20stimulate%20their%20integration%20into%20global%20value%20chains%20and%20increase%20the%20development%20benefits%20from%20multi-national%20company%20activities%20in%20their%20economies%20by%20aligning%20their%20policies%20to%20attract%20Foreign%20Direct%20Investment.%20The%20typology%20of%20industrial%20policies%20that%20countries%20can%20follow%20in%20enhancing%20global%20value%20chain%20participation%20includes%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.researchgate.net%2Fpublication%2F281901582_Global_Value_Chain-Oriented_Industrial_Policy_The_Role_of_Emerging_Economies%5C%22%3Ethree%20sets%20of%20policies%3C%2Fa%3E.%20These%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ficrier.org%2Fpdf%2FWorking_Paper_386.pdf%5C%22%3Ehorizontal%3C%2Fa%3E%20policies%20that%20affect%20the%20entire%20national%20economy%20(e.g.%20the%20Goods%20and%20Services%20Tax)%2C%20vertical%20industrial%20policies%20that%20are%20targeted%20at%20particular%20sectors%20or%20industries%20(e.g.%20Automotive%20Mission%20Plan%202016-26%20for%20the%20automobile%20industry)%2C%20and%20finally%2C%20global%20value%20chain-oriented%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20last%20type%20of%20policy%20could%20include%20the%20possibility%20of%20upgrading%20and%20improving%20the%20links%20across%20different%20segments%20of%20the%20value%20chain.%20India%E2%80%99s%20policy%20approach%20has%20been%20largely%20addressing%20logistical%20and%20infrastructure%20bottlenecks%20and%20improving%20the%20ease%20of%20doing%20business%2C%20and%20can%20be%20classified%20in%20terms%20of%20horizontal%20or%20vertical.%20However%2C%20what%20is%20needed%20for%20greater%20integration%20is%20global%20value%20chain-oriented%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EIndustrial%20policy%202.0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20times%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20resurgence%20of%20industrial%20policy%2C%20such%20as%20the%20Inflation%20Reduction%20Act%20of%20the%20United%20States%20and%2C%20in%20the%20Indian%20context%2C%20the%20recent%20production-linked%20incentive%20(PLI)%20schemes.%20These%20policies%20have%20been%20announced%20for%20fourteen%20sectors%20and%20could%20be%20extended%20to%20more%20in%20the%20future.%20They%20are%20India%E2%80%99s%20newest%20set%20of%20industrial%20policies%20after%20the%20earlier%20%E2%80%9CMake%20in%20India%E2%80%9D%20programme.%20Through%20these%20schemes%2C%20India%20is%20trying%20to%20attract%20FDI%20and%20create%20%E2%80%9Cchampion%20firms.%E2%80%9D%3Cb%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20Foreign%20Trade%20Policy%20announced%20earlier%20this%20year%20has%20the%20objective%20of%20integrating%20India%20into%20global%20value%20chains%20and%20making%20India%20an%20export%20hub.%20It%20is%20in%20this%20context%20that%20we%20need%20to%20see%20the%20PLI%20schemes%20aimed%20at%20improving%20the%20international%20competitiveness%20of%20the%20firms%20and%20increasing%20the%20localisation%20of%20Indian%20industries.%20The%20PLI%20schemes%20should%20also%20be%20seen%20in%20the%20context%20of%20global%20value%20chain-oriented%20policies%20aimed%20at%20increasing%20India%E2%80%99s%20global%20value%20chain%20integration.%20By%20trying%20to%20create%20champion%20firms%2C%20these%20policies%20are%20trying%20to%20pick%20%E2%80%9Cwinners%E2%80%9D%20which%20is%20in%20line%20with%20the%20objectives%20of%20industrial%20policy.%20However%2C%20it%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%20whether%20these%20firms%20will%20also%20become%20lead%20firms.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20line%20with%20the%20policy%20announcements%2C%20the%20tariffs%20on%20imported%20inputs%20have%20been%20increased%20to%20promote%20indigenous%20manufacturing.%20While%20these%20may%20work%20in%20the%20long%20run%2C%20in%20sectors%20where%20there%20is%20no%20capacity%20(e.g.%20solar%20panels%2C%20EV%20batteries)%2C%20the%20cost%20of%20production%20increases%20in%20the%20short%20run.%20What%20India%20is%20trying%E2%80%94through%20a%20combination%20of%20PLI%20schemes%20and%20import%20tariffs%20%E2%80%93%20is%20to%20create%20a%20larger%20part%20of%20the%20production%20chain%20within%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIf%20successful%2C%20India%20will%20have%20built%20a%20successful%20indigenous%20manufacturing%20base%20capable%20of%20exporting%2C%20too.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20if%20the%20manufacturing%20of%20the%20inputs%20does%20not%20become%20globally%20competitive%20despite%20the%20tariff%20protection%2C%20India%20will%20have%20lost%20the%20chance%20to%20integrate%20even%20the%20downstream%20industry%20into%20the%20value%20chains%20of%20%E2%80%9CFactory%20Asia.%E2%80%9D%20The%20distinction%20between%20industrial%20policy%20and%20import%20substitution%20needs%20to%20be%20understood.%20Import%20substitution%20can%20lead%20to%20greater%20reliance%20on%20domestically%20produced%20intermediates%20%E2%80%93%20thereby%20promoting%20indigenous%20manufacturing%20%E2%80%93%20but%20need%20not%20lead%20to%20greater%20global%20value%20chain%20integration.%20Hence%2C%20the%20objective%20of%20greater%20integration%20with%20global%20value%20chains%20through%20the%20PLI%20schemes%20is%20uncertain.%20Whether%20these%20policies%20will%20propel%20India%E2%80%99s%20manufacturing%20sector%20and%20help%20overcome%20the%20%E2%80%9Cjobless%20growth%E2%80%9D%20remains%20to%20be%20seen.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3ESaon%20Ray%20is%20an%20author%20and%20economist%20specialising%20in%20industry%20and%20international%20trade.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20first%20appeared%20in%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcasi.sas.upenn.edu%2Fiit%2Famritajash%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fcasi.sas.upenn.edu%2Fiit%2Fudayandas%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1697624538309000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw1hHpUZI4jlNYa6b8cG0NpI%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcasi.sas.upenn.edu%2Fiit%2Fudayandas%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndia%20in%20Transition%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20a%20publication%20of%20the%20Center%20for%20the%20Advanced%20Study%20of%20India%20(University%20of%20Pennsylvania).%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698484206000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F28143150%2Fpexels-andrey-matveev-4211136.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Findia-domestic-industrial-policy-global-value-chain%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20is%20among%20the%20countries%20that%20have%20used%20industrial%20policy%20to%20decouple%20from%20over-reliance%20on%20certain%20trading%20partners%20in%20recent%20times.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Findia-domestic-industrial-policy-global-value-chain%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Woman%20Sues%20Doctor%20Who%20Secretly%20Inseminated%20Her%20With%20His%20Sperm%2034%20Years%20Ago%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EA%20woman%20has%20sued%20a%20fertility%20doctor%20in%20Washington%2C%20alleging%20he%20secretly%20used%20his%20sperm%20for%20her%20artificial%20insemination%20procedure%2034%20years%20ago.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESharon%20Hayes%2C%20now%2067%2C%20from%20Hauser%20in%20the%20US%20state%20of%20Idaho%2C%20claims%20that%20she%20sought%20fertility%20treatment%20from%20Dr%20David%20R%20Claypool%2C%20an%20obstetrician%20and%20gynaecologist%20based%20in%20Spokane%2C%20Washington%2C%20back%20in%201989.%20This%20decision%20was%20made%20after%20she%20and%20her%20then-husband%20experienced%20difficulties%20in%20conceiving%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20in%20the%20Associated%20Press.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20complaint%20filed%20on%20Wednesday%20at%20the%20Spokane%20County%20Superior%20Court%2C%20Ms%20Hayes%20revealed%20her%20preference%20for%20an%20anonymous%20donor.%20However%2C%20Dr%20Claypool%20allegedly%20provided%20deceptive%20information%2C%20assuring%20her%20that%20the%20donor%20selection%20would%20be%20based%20on%20her%20specified%20traits%20such%20as%20hair%20and%20eye%20colour.%20He%20assured%20that%20the%20chosen%20donors%20would%20undergo%20health%20and%20genetic%20screenings.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20lawsuit%2C%20for%20each%20of%20several%20treatments%2C%20Dr%20Claypool%20charged%20%24100%20in%20cash%2C%20claiming%20these%20funds%20were%20meant%20for%20the%20college%20or%20medical%20students%20supposedly%20providing%20the%20sperm.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20wasn't%20until%20last%20year%20that%20her%2033-year-old%20daughter%2C%20Brianna%20Hayes%2C%20who%20was%20born%20from%20this%20procedure%2C%20discovered%20the%20identity%20of%20her%20biological%20father%20after%20submitting%20her%20DNA%20to%20the%20genetic%20testing%20and%20ancestry%20website%2C%2023andMe.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBrianna%20Hayes%20made%20another%20startling%20discovery%20that%20she%20had%20a%20minimum%20of%2016%20other%20half-siblings%20in%20the%20vicinity.%20It%20remains%20uncertain%20whether%20any%20other%20women%20are%20currently%20pursuing%20legal%20actions%20against%20Claypool.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20statement%2C%20Brianna%20Hayes%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt's%20been%20an%20identity%20crisis%2C%20for%20sure.%20This%20was%20hidden%20from%20me%20my%20whole%20life.%20I%20felt%20traumatised%20for%20my%20mom%2C%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20I'm%20a%20product%20of%20his%20actions%20is%20off-putting.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20conversation%20with%20one%20of%20his%20previous%20patients%2C%20Dr%20David%20R%20Claypool%20remarked%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20know%20people%20are%20very%20happy.%20But%20this%20is%20the%20first%20I've%20heard%20of%20anything%20in%2040%20years.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22pub