t%20month%20launched%20a%2015-point%20action%20plan%20to%20mitigate%20air%20pollution%20in%20the%20capital%20during%20the%20winter%20season%2C%20with%20a%20strong%20emphasis%20on%20addressing%20dust%20pollution%2C%20vehicular%20emissions%2C%20and%20the%20open%20burning%20of%20garbage.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpecial%20drives%20to%20check%20dust%2C%20vehicular%20and%20industrial%20pollution%20are%20already%20underway%20in%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20keeping%20with%20the%20practice%20of%20the%20last%20three%20years%2C%20Delhi%20had%20last%20month%20announced%20a%20comprehensive%20ban%20on%20the%20manufacture%2C%20storage%2C%20sale%2C%20and%20use%20of%20firecrackers%20within%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20public%20awareness%20campaign%2C%20'Patakhe%20Nahi%20Diye%20Jalao%2C'%20will%20soon%20be%20reintroduced%20to%20discourage%20firecracker%20burning.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20also%20prepared%20a%20pollution%20mitigation%20plan%20for%20each%20of%20the%2013%20identified%20pollution%20hotspots%20--%20Narela%2C%20Bawana%2C%20Mundka%2C%20Wazirpur%2C%20Rohini%2C%20R%20K%20Puram%2C%20Okhla%2C%20Jahangirpuri%2C%20Anand%20Vihar%2C%20Punjabi%20Bagh%2C%20Mayapuri%2C%20Dwarka.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERai%20recently%20said%20the%20government%20has%20identified%20eight%20more%20pollution%20hotspots%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20existing%2013%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20and%20special%20teams%20will%20be%20deployed%20there%20to%20check%20pollution%20sources.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20government%20has%20also%20decided%20to%20use%20suppressant%20powder%20to%20prevent%20dust%20pollution%20in%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDust%20suppressants%20could%20include%20chemical%20agents%20like%20calcium%20chloride%2C%20magnesium%20chloride%2C%20lignosulfonates%20and%20various%20polymers.%20These%20chemicals%20work%20by%20attracting%20and%20binding%20fine%20dust%20particles%20together%2C%20making%20them%20too%20heavy%20to%20become%20airborne.%3Cbr%3E%20%C2