E%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20instance%2C%20he%20said%2C%20a%20handful%20of%20Ukrainian%20soldiers%20fended%20off%20hundreds%20of%20Russian%20troops.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYesterday%20Sam%20flew%20the%20plane%20and%20said%20that%20just%20eight%20people%20were%20sitting%20in%20the%20trench%2C%20just%20eight%20khohols.%20And%20our%20men%20go%20there%20by%20the%20hundreds%2C%20and%20they%20are%20not%20even%20capable%20of%20taking%20a%20fucking%20thing!%26quot%3B%C2%A0he%20said.%20%26quot%3BKhohols%26quot%3B%20is%20derogatory%20Russian%20term%20for%20Ukrainians.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20snipers%20and%20machine%20gunners%20were%20in%20the%20trench%2C%20along%20with%20a%20%26quot%3Bpillbox%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20a%20concrete%20dug-in%20guard%20post%20%E2%80%94%20to%20protect%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInsider%20was%20not%20able%20to%20independently%20verify%20the%20authenticity%20of%20the%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine's%20intelligence%20department%20has%20periodically%20published%20the%20audios%20of%20intercepted%20Russian%20calls%2C%20which%20Russian%20media%20often%20dismisses%20as%20fake.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussia%20has%20been%20conducting%20attacks%20on%20Ukrainian%20positions%20in%20the%20town%20of%20Ivanivka%20as%20they%20try%20to%20push%20forward%20toward%20Kupyansk%20in%20Kharkiv%20Oblast%2C%20Ukrainian%20officials%20have%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20spokesperson%20for%20Ukraine's%20Ground%20Forces%20Command%2C%20Lieutenant%20Colonel%20Volodymyr%20Fitio%2C%20said%20that%20they%20expected%20Russia%20to%20try%20and%20recapture%20Kupyansk%2C%20so%20%26quot%3Bappropriate%20defense%20structures%20were%20built%2C%26quot%3B%20per%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ukrinform.net%2Frubric-ato%2F3778957-russia-amasses-about-100000-soldiers-in-lymankupyansk-direction.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUkrinform%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessins