0to%20her%20at%20a%20party.%20Sharma%20subsequently%20engaged%20in%20improper%20communications%20and%20deleted%20messages%20before%20his%20arrest.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Findian-origin-ex-cop-found-guilty-of-misconduct-barred-from-policing-in-uk%2Farticleshow%2F104776676.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Findian-origin-ex-cop-found-guilty-of-misconduct-barred-from-policing-in-uk%2Famp_articleshow%2F104776676.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Findian-origin-ex-cop-found-guilty-of-misconduct-barred-from-policing-in-uk%2Famp_articleshow%2F104776676.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22It%20Is%20Not%20Civil%20Servants%E2%80%99%20Job%20to%20%E2%80%98Showcase%E2%80%99%20Govt%20Achievements%3A%20Former%20Cabinet%20Secretary%20Chandrasekhar%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F28134832%2Fkm-chand.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20order%20to%20deploy%20civil%20servants%20as%20%E2%80%98Rath%20Prabharis%E2%80%99%20to%20specifically%20promote%20the%20%E2%80%9Cachievements%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20past%20nine%20years%20has%20drawn%20significant%20criticism%20from%20several%20quarters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmodi-government-move-to-turn-government-officers-into-rath-prabharis-stirs-storm%5C%22%3Eorder%3C%2Fa%3E%20asks%20every%20ministry%20to%20nominate%20officers%20of%20the%20level%20of%20joint%20secretaries%20and%20below%20in%20each%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20765%20districts%C2%A0to%20%E2%80%9Cshowcase%20the%20achievements%20of%20the%20last%20nine%20years%20of%20Government%20of%20India%E2%80%9D%20between%20November%2020%2C%202023%20and%20January%2025%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESome%20retired%20bureaucrats%20have%20said%20that%20this%20amounts%20to%20the%20wholesale%20politicisation%20of%20the%20civil%20services%2C%20and%20registered%20their%20protest.%20While%20the%20government%20has%20said%20that%20Rath%20Prabharis%20will%20not%20be%20nominated%20in%20the%20five%20states%20headed%20to%20assembly%20polls%20until%20the%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct%20is%20in%20place%2C%20this%20will%20only%20provide%20temporary%20relief%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Frath-prabhari-illegal-wholesale-politicisation-civil-services-eas-sarma%5C%22%3Eformer%20IAS%20officer%20E.A.S.%20Sarma%20said%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20spoke%20to%20K.M.%20Chandrasekhar%2C%20who%20retired%20as%20cabinet%20secretary%20in%202011%20and%20served%20under%20Manmohan%20Singh%2C%20about%20his%20views%20on%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20do%20you%20view%20this%20order%3F%20Would%20you%20say%20this%20is%20a%20violation%20of%20the%20Central%20Civil%20Services%20Conduct%20Rules%2C%201964%20which%20says%20government%20servants%20will%20not%20indulge%20in%20political%20activities%3F%20This%20is%20an%20allegation%20being%20made%20by%20opposition%20leaders.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20would%20say%20this%20is%20not%20a%20violation%20of%20the%20conduct%20rules%2C%20because%20government%20servants%20are%20supposed%20to%20follow%20orders%20unless%20they%20are%20against%20the%20law.%20But%20it%20is%20certainly%20not%20in%20good%20taste.%20A%20civil%20servant%E2%80%99s%20job%20is%20to%20implement%20government%20schemes%20and%20deliver%20services.%20At%20best%2C%20if%20there%20are%20issues%20of%20coordination%20with%20the%20states%2C%20officers%20can%20put%20out%20their%20contact%20details%20but%20that%20is%20for%20the%20purposes%20of%20carrying%20out%20their%20duties.%20As%20cabinet%20secretary%2C%20I%20would%20take%20secretaries%20of%20various%20departments%20by%20the%20planeloads%20to%20the%20various%20states%2C%20especially%20the%20weaker%20states%20for%20better%20coordination%20between%20the%20Union%20and%20state%20governments%20and%20better%20delivery%20of%20services.%20We%20would%20resolve%20problems%20on%20the%20spot.%20That%20in%20short%20is%20the%20job%20of%20a%20civil%20servant.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBut%20politicians%20like%20BJP%20IT%20Cell%20head%20Amit%20Malviya%20say%20that%20bureaucrats%20must%20serve%20the%20people%20as%20the%20government%20deems%20fit.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOur%20job%20is%20not%20to%20showcase%20or%20celebrate%20the%20achievements%20of%20the%20government.%20While%20this%20order%20of%20Rath%20Prabharis%20is%20per%20se%20not%20illegal%2C%20it%20is%20definitely%20in%20bad%20taste.%20Projecting%20anyone%20in%20this%20manner%20is%20extraordinary%20and%20I%20have%20never%20heard%20of%20something%20like%20this%20in%20my%20entire%20career.%20Anyway%2C%20officials%20at%20the%20level%20of%20deputy%20director%20or%20director%20are%20too%20junior%20and%20have%20the%20power%20to%20only%20put%20up%20files.%20They%20cannot%20take%20a%20decision%20or%20resolve%20a%20problem%20on%20the%20ground.%20So%20just%20reading%20out%20from%20a%20written%20piece%20of%20paper%20is%20not%20something%20that%20officers%20should%20be%20doing.%20This%20is%20most%20unusual.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThere%20is%20another%20order%20issued%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Defence%20which%20says%20that%20soldiers%20on%20leave%20must%20showcase%20the%20efforts%20of%20the%20government.%20So%20this%20is%20not%20just%20about%20government%20servants.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20again%20is%20a%20ridiculous%20order.%20When%20a%20person%20is%20on%20leave%2C%20they%20cannot%20be%20tasked%20to%20carry%20out%20such%20orders.%20The%20government%20can%20only%20request.%20And%20even%20then%2C%20how%20can%20such%20an%20order%20be%20implemented%3F%20Who%20will%20monitor%20and%20how%20will%20the%20soldier%20know%20the%20fine%20details%20of%20the%20schemes%20of%20the%20government%3F%20If%20a%20person%20is%20on%20leave%2C%20he%20or%20she%20is%20on%20leave.%20If%20a%20person%20is%20asked%20to%20carry%20out%20these%20orders%20then%20he%20or%20she%20cannot%20be%20deemed%20to%20be%20on%20leave.%20Again%20a%20highly%20improper%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIf%20you%20were%20cabinet%20secretary%20now%2C%20what%20would%20you%20do%3F%20And%20it%20is%20easy%20to%20criticise%20when%20an%20officer%20has%20retired%20but%20it%20is%20quite%20a%20different%20thing%20when%20the%20officer%20is%20serving.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20can%20only%20share%20an%20anecdote%20of%20what%20it%20was%20like%20to%20work%20with%20the%20Manmohan%20Singh%20government.%20Once%20I%20called%20the%20prime%20minister%20about%20an%20appointment%20of%20a%20special%20director%20to%20the%20CBI.%20A%20junior%20officer%20was%20being%20appointed%2C%20overlooking%20the%20seniority%20of%20another.%20The%20prime%20minister%20was%20eating%20lunch.%20He%20halted%20his%20meal%2C%20heard%20me%20out%20and%20left%20his%20lunch%20unfinished.%20A%20few%20minutes%20later%2C%20I%20got%20a%20call%20from%20(the%20advisor%20to%20the%20prime%20minister)%20T.K.A.%20Nair%2C%20who%20said%20the%20prime%20minister%20wanted%20to%20see%20the%20two%20of%20us.%20We%20reached%207%2C%20Race%20Course%20Road%2C%20where%20Pulok%20Chatterjee%20(also%20principal%20secretary%20to%20the%20prime%20minister)%20was%20already%20waiting.%20The%20prime%20minister%20immediately%20worked%20out%20a%20solution%20to%20the%20satisfaction%20of%20the%20senior%20CBI%20officer%20and%20gave%20orders%20to%20the%20Department%20of%20Personnel%20and%20Training%20Minister%20Prithviraj%20Chavan%20to%20do%20the%20needful.%20I%20am%20not%20sure%20if%20anyone%20can%20even%20tell%20the%20present%20prime%20minister%20that%20he%20is%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698481545000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2