%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWith%20as%20many%20as%2014%20ports%20and%20terminals%2C%20the%20Adani%20Group%20handles%20a%20quarter%20of%20all%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fbusiness%2Fcompanies%2Fadani-ports-handles-highest-ever-rail-cargo-fy23-8613993%2F%5C%22%3Ecargo%20passing%20through%20India%E2%80%99s%20ports%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexpress-exclusive%2Fon-average-an-adani-port-every-500-km-of-coastline-these-handle-24-of-all-cargo-govt-share-dips-9002772%2F%5C%22%3Ethe%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reported.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlong%20India%E2%80%99s%205%2C422-kilometre%20coastline%2C%20Adani%20has%20a%20presence%20every%20500%20km%20on%20an%20average%2C%20from%20just%20a%20blip%20on%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20far%20western%20end%2010%20years%20ago%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThree%20top%20officials%2C%20including%20a%20former%20competition%20regulator%2C%20have%20flagged%20risks%20of%20market%20concentration%20in%20the%20ports%20industry%2C%20highlighting%20Adani%E2%80%99s%20phenomenal%20expansion%20in%20the%20last%2010%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%2010%20years%2C%20the%20total%20cargo%20handled%20by%20Adani%20ports%20jumped%20nearly%20fourfold%20to%20337%20million%20tonnes%20in%20FY23.%20Its%20volumes%20grew%20at%20a%20compounded%20annual%20growth%20rate%20of%2014%25%20against%20the%20industry%E2%80%99s%204%25.%20If%20Adani%E2%80%99s%20share%20is%20removed%2C%20the%20latter%20figure%20falls%20to%20barely%202.7%25%2C%20the%20newspaper%20said%20in%20its%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20group%E2%80%99s%20market%20share%20in%20total%20cargo%20handled%20has%20nearly%20tripled%20from%20around%209%25%20in%202013%20to%20about%2024%25%20in%202023%3B%20that%20of%20Central%20government-controlled%20ports%20dropped%20to%20around%2054.5%25%20from%2058.5%25%20in%202013.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmongst%20ports%20that%20are