20indicated%20that%20inflation%20will%20have%20to%20be%20watched%20more%20carefully%2C%20following%20the%20Hamas-Israel%20war%20and%20its%20potential%20spread%20to%20the%20broader%20West%20Asia%20region.%20This%20is%20not%20particularly%20good%20news%20for%20ruling%20regimes%20across%20the%20world%20which%20are%20approaching%20general%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20markets%20may%20not%20take%20kindly%20to%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20excessive%20bellicosity%20towards%20UN%20Secretary%20General%20Ant%C3%B3nio%20Guterres%2C%20who%20is%20pressing%20for%20the%20observance%20of%20international%20law%20and%20the%20rules%20of%20war.%20The%20markets%20are%20psychologically%20impacted%20by%20words%20used%20by%20top%20global%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20Ukraine%2C%209%2C600%20civilians%20were%20killed%20over%2018%20months.%20In%20Gaza%20already%207%2C000%20plus%20civilians%20are%20dead%20in%20a%20few%20weeks%20in%20the%20most%20destructive%20bombing%20in%20a%20short%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20advising%20Israel%20to%20eschew%20rage%20in%20its%20response%20may%20have%20caused%20nervousness%20in%20the%20markets.%20If%20Israel%20continues%20to%20act%20aggressively%20over%20the%20next%20few%20weeks%2C%20sharpening%20the%20brinkmanship%20between%20the%20Western%20powers%20and%20the%20Iran-Russia-China%20axis%2C%20one%20could%20well%20witness%20another%20round%20of%20spikes%20in%20inflation%20and%20interest%20rates%20globally.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESome%20reputed%20Wall%20Street%20analysts%20have%20made%20the%20contrarian%20argument%20that%20the%20markets%20are%20taking%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20war%20in%20their%20stride%20and%20there%20is%20some%20optimism%20that%20it%20won%E2%80%99t%20spread%20to%20the%20larger%20region.%20Perhaps%20this%20optimism%20flows%20from%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20war%20avoided%20the%20worst%20economic%20consequences%20simply%20because%20nations%20ranged%20against%20each%20other%20chose%20to%20minimise%20damage%20by%20letting%20Russian%20oil%20come%20into%20markets%20via%20the%20backdoor.%20Surely%20there%20was%20an%20economic%20backlash%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20hardening%20inflation%20and%20interest%20rates%2C%20but%20the%20worst-case%20scenario%20was%20avoided.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20hope%20that%20a%20similar%20cycle%20may%20play%20out%20during%20a%20prolonged%20Israel-Palestine%20conflict.%20It%20is%20true%20that%20the%20powerful%20political-business%20elites%20in%20the%20US%2C%20Europe%2C%20China%2C%20Russia%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20Iran%20and%20Israel%20are%20heavily%20invested%20in%20global%20financial%20assets%20and%20their%20instinct%20would%20be%20to%20minimise%20economic%20damage.%20But%20as%20President%20Biden%20observed%2C%20any%20response%20characterised%20by%20rage%20and%20vengefulness%20could%20upset%20such%20rational%20calculations.%20The%20collective%20market%20intelligence%20is%20well%20aware%20of%20this%2C%20too.%20Things%20can%20easily%20spiral%20out%20of%20control%20in%20a%20war%20that%20increasingly%20becomes%20part%20of%20big%20powers%20rivalry.%20Such%20accidents%20do%20occur%20in%20history.%20Hence%20the%20continuing%20nervousness%20seen%20in%20the%20behaviour%20of%20stocks%2C%20bonds%2C%20crude%20and%20gold%2C%20all%20of%20which%20can%20have%20a%20profound%20impact%20on%20the%20real%20economy.%20India%20will%20not%20be%20insulated%20from%20this.%20A%20lot%20of%20foreign%20institutional%20money%20has%20left%20the%20Indian%20stock%20market%20in%20the%20past%20several%20weeks.%20Foreign%20equity%20money%20is%20leaving%20most%20emerging%20markets%20in%20search%20of%20safer%20investment%20options.%20US%20bonds%20are%20seen%20as%20offering%20good%20risk-free%20returns.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EForeign%20direct%20investment%20(FDI)%20into%20India%20has%20also%20slowed%20down%20considerably%20because%20events%20like%20Ukraine%20and%20Gaza%20urge%20global%20investors%20to%20hold%20back%20until%20there%20is%20clarity%20