20in%20the%20early%20morning%20hours%20of%20October%2028%2C%20following%20weeks%20of%20mobilization.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIsrael%20Defense%20Forces%20officials%20so%20far%20have%20declined%20to%20confirm%20the%20actions%20are%20part%20of%20an%20anticipated%20full-scale%20ground%20invasion%2C%20but%20multiple%20reports%20indicate%20a%20sharp%20increase%20in%20IDF%20troops%20advancing%20across%20the%20border%20into%20Gaza%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20explosions%20from%20continuous%20airstrikes.%20Internet%20and%20cellular%20service%20has%20been%20cut%20off%20in%20the%20region%2C%20limiting%20firsthand%20reports%20on%20the%20ground.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20offensive%20is%20Israel's%20most%20brutal%20response%20yet%20to%20the%20deadly%20Hamas%20terror%20attacks%20on%20October%207%20that%20claimed%20more%20than%201%2C400%20lives%20and%20resulted%20in%20100-200%20people%20being%20kidnapped%20and%20taken%20to%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20Israel%20has%20waged%20an%20intense%20bombing%20campaign%20across%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20and%20said%20it%20would%20not%20relent%20until%20Hamas%20released%20all%20hostages%20who%20were%20taken%20during%20the%20initial%20October%207%20attacks.%20The%20militant%20group%20has%20said%20that%20it%20would%20release%20the%20hostages%20if%20Israel%20ceased%20its%20counteroffensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20advisor%20to%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20warned%20of%20the%20ground%20invasion%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FNTarnopolsky%2Fstatus%2F1717989419125182813%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etelling%20MSNBC's%20Katy%20Tur%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Friday%20that%20%26quot%3Btonight%20we%20are%20starting%20payback.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20October%2027%2C%20internet%20and%20cellular%20services%20were%20cut%20off%20in%20Gaza%2C%20and%20the%20emergency%20number%2C%20101%2C%20was%20also%20down%2C%20meaning%20that%20ambulances%20could%20not%20be%20dispatched.%20Medical%20workers%20also%20said%20they%20could%20not%20communicate%20with%20each%20other%2C%20and%20multiple%20news%20outlets%20said%20they%20had%20lost%20contact%20with%20reporters%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Hamas-run%20Palestinian%20health%20ministry%20said%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fisrael-hamas-war-gaza-health-ministry-health-death-toll-59470820308b31f1faf73c703400b033%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20than%207%2C000%20Gazans%20have%20died%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%20Israel%20launched%20its%20counter-assault%20and%20that%20nearly%203%2C000%20were%20minors.%20The%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newscientist.com%2Farticle%2Fdn25993-the-reasons-why-gazas-population-is-so-young%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emedian%20age%20in%20Gaza%20is%2018%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDefense%20Minister%20Yoav%20Gallant%20said%20Israel%20expects%20a%20long%20and%20difficult%20ground%20offensive%20into%20Gaza.%20It%20%26quot%3Bwill%20take%20a%20long%20time%26quot%3B%20to%20dismantle%20Hamas'%20vast%20network%20of%20tunnels%2C%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20expects%20a%20lengthy%20phase%20of%20lower-intensity%20fighting%20as%20Israel%20destroys%20%26quot%3Bpockets%20of%20resistance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20comments%20pointed%20to%20a%20potentially%20grueling%20and%20open-ended%20new%20phase%20of%20the%20war%20after%20three%20weeks%20of%20relentless%20bombardment.%20Israel%20has%20said%20it%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fisrael-hamas-palestinians-gaza-biden-65427884b38bac77249f280fa8c796c8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaims%20to%20crush%20Hamas'%20rule%20in%20Gaza%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20its%20ability%20to%20threaten%20Israel.%20But%20how%20Hamas'%20defeat%20will%20be%20measured%20and%20an%20invasion's%20endgame%20remains%20unclear.%20Israel%20says%20it%20does%20not%20intend%20to%20rule%20the%20tiny%20territory%20but%20not%20who%20it%20expects%20to%20govern%20%E2%80%94%20even%20as%20Gallant%20suggested%20a%20long-term%20insurgency%20could%20ensue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Washington%2C%20the%20Pentagon%20said%20US%20Defense%20Secretary%20Lloyd%20Austin%20spoke%20with%20Gallant%20on%20Friday%20and%20%26quot%3Bunderscored%20the%20importance%20of%20protecting%20civilians%20during%20the%20Israel%20Defense%20Forces'%20operations%20and%20focusing%20on%20the%20urgency%20of%20humanitarian%20aid%20delivery%20for%20civilians%20in%20Gaza.%26quot%3B%20The%20Pentagon%20said%20Austin%20also%20brought%20up%20%26quot%3Bthe%20need%20for%20Hamas%20to%20release%20all%20of%20the%20hostages.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20conflict%20has%20threatened%20to%20ignite%20a%20wider%20war%20across%20the%20region.%20Arab%20nations%20%E2%80%94%20including%20U.S.%20allies%20and%20ones%20that%20have%20reached%20peace%20deals%20or%20normalized%20ties%20with%20Israel%20%E2%80%94%20have%20raised%20increasing%20alarm%20over%20a%20potential%20ground%20invasion%2C%20likely%20to%20bring%20even%20higher%20casualties%20amid%20urban%20fighting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESalem%20Ahmad%20Ammar%2C%20a%20Gaza%20resident%20speaking%20near%20Al%20Aqsa%20Martyrs%20Hospital%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2023%2F10%2F27%2Fmiddleeast%2Fisrael-gaza-ground-operations-airstrike-intl%2Findex.html%5C%22%3ECNN%3C%2Fa%3E%20he%20and%20his%20wife%20have%20split%20up%20as%20they%20try%20to%20wait%20out%20the%20fighting%2C%20hoping%20that%20one%20of%20them%20may%20survive%20the%20onslaught%20to%20take%20care%20of%20their%20children.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20data-component-name%3D%5C%22paragraph%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%22cms.cnn.com%2F_components%2Fparagraph%2Finstances%2Fclo968azw00063b6i444dxbqi%40published%5C%22%20data-analytics-observe%3D%5C%22off%5C%22%20data-editable%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%20data-article-gutter%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BDon't%20know%20if%20I%20(will)%20live%20to%20see%20the%20daylight%20tomorrow%20morning%2C%26quot%3B%20Ammar%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20split%20from%20my%20wife%2C%20and%20the%20kids%20went%20to%20her%20parents'%20house%2C%20and%20I%20came%20to%20the%20hospital%20here%20in%20the%20event%20we%20die%20in%20different%20places%20and%20maybe%20one%20of%20us%20would%20live%20and%20our%20kids%20will%20live.%20Difficult%20choices%20we%20are%20making.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20data-component-name%3D%5C%22paragraph%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%22cms.cnn.com%2F_components%2Fparagraph%2Finstances%2Fclo968azw00063b6i444dxbqi%40published%5C%22%20data-analytics-observe%3D%5C%22off%5C%22%20data-editable%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%20data-article-gutter%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3EThough%20120%20countries%2C%20an%20overwhelming%20majority%20of%20the%20United%20Nations%2C%20voted%20Friday%20for%20a%20resolution%20to%20call%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Bsustained%20humanitarian%20truce%26quot%3B%20in%20Gaza%2C%20Israel%20has%20so%20far%20refused%20international%20calls%20for%20a%20cease-fire.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20data-component-name%3D%5C%22paragraph%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%22cms.cnn.com%2F_components%2Fparagraph%2Finstances%2Fclo968azw00063b6i444dxbqi%40published%5C%22%20data-analytics-observe%3D%5C%22off%5C%22%20data-editable%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%20data-article-gutter%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3EThe%20US%2C%20one%20of%20the%20nation's%20closest%20allies%2C%20has%20not%20formally%20issued%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhich-lawmakers-voted-against-israel-resolution-hamas-attacks-progressives-2023-10%5C%22%3Edeclaration%20for%20a%20cease-fire%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-increase-force-posture-middle-east-amid-israel-hamas-war-2023-10%5C%22%3Eincreased%20its%20force%20posture%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20region%20amid%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20war%2C%20redirecting%20Navy%20strike%20groups%20and%20activating%20Patriot%20battalions%20to%20aid%20in%20the%20defense%20of%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E