0Delhi%2C%20scholars%20have%20been%20particularly%20exercised%20about%20the%20fate%20of%20the%20National%20Museum.%20Shockingly%2C%20close%20to%2070%20years%20after%20it%20opened%20in%201955%2C%20a%20complete%20inventory%20of%20its%20holdings%20is%20still%20not%20available%20in%20the%20public%20domain.%20Nor%20is%20there%20any%20clarity%20from%20the%20government%20about%20when%20the%20existing%20museum%20will%20be%20closed%20to%20visitors%3B%20where%20its%20priceless%20contents%20will%20be%20housed%20while%20the%20current%20building%20is%20demolished%20and%20before%20the%20new%20premises%20are%20ready%3B%20how%20long%20it%20will%20take%20for%20the%20North%20and%20South%20Block%20to%20be%20refurbished%20and%20repurposed%3B%20how%20and%20where%20researchers%20will%20have%20access%20to%20the%20museum%E2%80%99s%20artefacts%20during%20the%20transition%2C%20and%20what%2C%20if%20any%20steps%20will%20be%20taken%20to%20ensure%20that%20nothing%20is%20lost%2C%20stolen%20or%20damaged%20in%20the%20move.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20National%20Museum%2C%20like%20most%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20central%20and%20state%20museums%2C%20is%20significantly%20understaffed.%20How%20a%20change%20of%20address%20will%20be%20managed%20without%20adequate%20personnel%20is%20anybody%E2%80%99s%20guess.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F05123902%2F2268292509_c6a540e595_b.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F05123902%2F2268292509_c6a540e595_b.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F05123902%2F2268292509_c6a540e595_b-300x225.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-678384%5C%22