0personality%20as%20the%20RSS%20boss%2C%20would%20detect%20%E2%80%9Cwokeism%E2%80%9D%20intruding%20India%20%E2%80%93%20that%20too%20at%20a%20time%20when%20we%20are%20so%20thankfully%20counting%20the%20blessings%20of%20%E2%80%98Amrit%20Kaal%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECould%20it%2C%20then%2C%20be%20that%20the%20Big%20Boss%E2%80%99s%20Dussehra%20oration%20was%20sourced%20out%20of%20Nagpur%3F%20Not%20just%20out%20of%20Nagpur%20but%20possibly%20out%20of%20India%3F%20Only%20a%20highly%20%E2%80%9CAmericanised%E2%80%9D%20speechwriter%20or%20an%20NRI%20domiciled%20in%20Chicago%20or%20Atlanta%20could%20think%20that%20%E2%80%9Cwoke%E2%80%9D%20would%20be%20of%20any%20concern%20or%20relevance%20to%20anyone%20in%20India.%20It%20can%20be%20safely%20asserted%20that%20even%20the%20editorial%20writers%20in%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EOrganiser%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Estable%20would%20be%20at%20a%20loss%20to%20explain%20or%20define%20these%20%E2%80%9Cwoke%E2%80%9D%20subversives%2C%20out%20to%20deny%20Mother%20India%20its%20glorious%20past%2C%20present%20and%20future.%20And%2C%20it%20can%20be%20confidently%20argued%20that%20no%20BJP%20operative%20in%20Bhagalpur%20or%20Bathinda%20or%20Bhavnagar%20will%20have%20any%20idea%20what%20the%20RSS%20boss%20was%20talking%20about.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%2C%20pray%2C%20who%20in%20god%E2%80%99s%20name%20are%20these%20%E2%80%9Ccultural%20Marxists%2C%E2%80%9D%20still%20breathing%20fire%20and%20brimstone%20even%20after%20nine%20years%20of%20a%20%3Cem%3Edanda%20sarkar%3C%2Fem%3E%3F%20How%20have%20they%20dared%20to%20escape%20detection%20from%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20sniffing%20Labrador%20retrievers%3F%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20this%20year%E2%80%99s%20Dusshera%20speech%20has%20not%20evoked%20any%20kind%20of%20serious%20interest%20or%20reaction%2C%20perhaps%20it%20is%20because%20something%20is%20seriously%20wrong-keyed%20in%20Mohan%20Bhagwat%E2%80%99s%20ruminations.%20It%20was%20a%20total%20washout%2C%20compared%20to%20the%20animated%20critiques%20and%20salutations%20Bhagwat%20has%20received%20in%20the%20past.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECould%20it%20be%20that%20Bhagwat%E2%80%99s%20listlessness%20reflects%20a%20definite%20resolution%20of%20the%20RSS-BJP%20equation%20after%20nearly%20two%20decades%20of%20sparring%20and%20jostling%3F%20Remember%20how%20BJP%20president%20L.K.%20Advani%20was%20defenestrated%20out%20of%20office%20after%20he%20made%20his%20vastly%20misunderstood%20speech%20on%20Mohammed%20Ali%20Jinnah%20during%20his%20visit%20to%20Pakistan%20in%20mid-2005%3F%20A%20BJP%20president%20had%20no%20choice%20but%20to%20bow%20to%20the%20Nagpur%20bosses%E2%80%99%20diktat%20and%20put%20in%20his%20papers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERemember%2C%20also%2C%20Advani%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Fmagazine%2Fnation%2Fstory%2F20051003-leadership-crisis-deepens-in-bjp-as-lk-advani-prepares-to-step-down-786801-2005-10-02%5C%22%3Epithy%20observations%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20that%20time%3A%20%E2%80%9CLately%20an%20impression%20has%20gained%20ground%20that%20no%20political%20or%20organisational%20decision%20can%20be%20taken%20without%20the%20consent%20of%20the%20RSS%20functionaries.%20This%20perception%2C%20we%20hold%2C%20will%20do%20no%20good%20either%20to%20the%20party%20or%20to%20the%20RSS.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBhagwat%E2%80%99s%20Dussehra%20speech%20this%20year%20is%20the%20final%20conclusive%20evidence%20that%20the%20matter%20between%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20RSS%20has%20been%20settled%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20Modi-Shah%20duo.%20He%20mouthed%20a%20meandering%20defence%20of%20all%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20has%20done%20or%20not%20done%20these%20last%20nine%20years.%20He%20seems%20to%20have%20enlisted%20himself%20in%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20favourite%20political%20game%20of%20inventing%20enemies.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20seems%20that%20the%20RSS%20chief%20has%20allowed%20himself%20to%20be%20overimpressed%2C%20perhaps%20even%20overawed%2C%20not%20just%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20but%20even%20by%20home%20minister%20Shah.%20Bhagwat%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frss-chief-mohan-bhagwat-how-did-manipur-violence-continue-unabated-despite-a-strong-government%5C%22%3Eallegation%20of%20external%20forces%3C%2Fa%3E%20muddying%20the%20ethnic%20fault%20lines%20in%20Manipur%20is%20not%20worthy%20of%20an%20organisation%20chief%20who%20takes%20considerable%20pride%20in%20its%20ability%20to%20keep%20itself%20clinically%20insulated%20from%20the%20politicians%E2%80%99%20dirty%20world%20and%20to%20think%20clear-headedly%20about%20national%20interests.%20Of%20course%2C%20external%20forces%20have%20always%20meddled%20and%20will%20continue%20to%20try%20to%20meddle%20in%20our%20affairs%2C%20but%20it%20is%20precisely%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20primary%20task%20to%20protect%20us%20from%20such%20inimical%20elements.%20Yet%2C%20Bhagwat%20seeks%20to%20exculpate%20the%20home%20minister%E2%80%99s%20glorious%20administrative%20and%20political%20failure%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBemoaning%20is%20not%20an%20option%20for%20any%20government%2C%20certainly%20not%20for%20a%20regime%20that%20boasts%20of%20a%2056-inch%20%3Cem%3Echhaathi%3C%2Fem%3E.%20It%20is%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20obligation%20to%20summon%20the%20requisite%20wisdom%20and%20policies%20to%20prevent%20the%20kind%20of%20bloodbath%20that%20has%20been%20witnessed%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmohan-bhagwat-comments-manipur-violence-northeast-puzzle%5C%22%3EMohan%20Bhagwat%E2%80%99s%20Comments%20on%20Manipur%20Violence%20Show%20Northeast%20Remains%20a%20Puzzle%20That%20RSS%20Can%E2%80%99t%20Solve%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnlike%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%2C%20who%20did%20not%20care%20to%20appease%20the%20Nagpur%20bosses%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20has%20defanged%20the%20commissars%20of%20the%20saffron%20brotherhood%20by%20very%20adroitly%20co-opting%20these%20supposed%20men%20of%20%E2%80%98integrity%E2%80%99%20in%20his%20transactional%20regime.%20The%20swayamsevak-cum-pracharak%20is%20now%20contaminated%20with%20the%20poisoned%20spoils%20of%20power.%20This%20ethical%20degeneration%20has%20bubbled%20up%20all%20the%20way%20to%20the%20Nagpur%20brass.%20All%20the%20vim%20and%20vigour%20has%20been%20drained%20out%20of%20the%20RSS%E2%80%99s%20role%20as%20a%20watchful%20guardian%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20morals%20and%20manners.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20taming%20of%20the%20Bhagwat-led%20RSS%20is%20not%20without%20its%20ramifications%20for%20the%20ruling%20party%E2%80%99s%20power%20landscape.%20All%20those%20who%20believe%20that%20this%20%E2%80%98parent%E2%80%99%20organisation%20will%20be%20able%20to%20shape%20and%20determine%20the%20post-Modi%20arrangements%20may%20find%20themselves%20totally%20wrong-footed.%20In%20the%20immediate%20months%20to%20come%2C%20the%20RSS%20cannot%20be%20counted%20upon%20to%20be%20a%20source%20of%20restraint%20and%20sobriety%20as%20the%20oversized%20Modi%20personality%20cult%20goes%20into%20overdrive.%20The%20polity%E2%80%99s%20equilibrium%20is%20set%20to%20get%20further%20tilted%20in%20favour%20of%20rampant%20authoritarian%20tendencies.%20So%20much%20for%20happy%20days.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698454666000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F27145611%2FF9Lc8o2aYAAiOW1.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fa-listless-bhagwat-is-advantage-modi%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20RSS%20chief%20warning%20against%20%E2%80%9Ccultural%20Marxists%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cwoke%E2%80%9D%2