2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMultiple%20Sclerosis%20(MS)%20is%20a%20potentially%20disabling%20disease%20of%20the%20brain%20and%20spinal%20cord%2C%20as%20per%20the%20Mayo%20Clinic.%20Undeterred%20and%20enthusiastic%2C%20Sudha%20continued%20giving%20back%20to%20the%20community%20by%20opening%20her%20home%20to%20numerous%20kids%20and%20teachers%20over%20the%20years%20to%20forge%20a%20bond%20in%20creativity%2C%20friendship%20and%20activity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESeated%20around%20Sudha%20and%20recollecting%20the%20happy%20times%2C%20teachers%20of%20the%20camp%2C%20Jayashree%20Prasad%2C%20Srimathi%20K%20Singh%20and%20Mamatha%20talk%20about%20how%20important%20these%20summer%20camps%20were%20for%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSudha%20was%20the%20fulcrum%20around%20which%20we%20functioned%2C%20we%20love%20her%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20teachers%20say%2C%20echoing%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20960px)%20100vw%2C%20960px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FIMG-20230928-WA0004_11zon-1698072330.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20kids%20at%20the%20camp%20participating%20in%20an%20event.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FIMG-20230928-WA0004_11zon-1698072330.jpg%20960w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FIMG-20230928-WA0004_11zon-1698072330-225x300.jpg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FIMG-20230928-WA0004_11zon-1698072330-500x667.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FIMG-20230928-WA0004_11zon-1698072330-768x1024.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FIMG-20230928-WA0004_11zon-1698072330-640x853.jpg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FIMG-20230928-WA0004_11zon-1698072330-150x200.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-332872%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20kids%20at%20the%20camp%20participating%20in%20an%20event.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20the%20summer%20camp%20took%20roots%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EHailing%20from%20a%20reputed%20family%20and%20marrying%20into%20another%2C%20Sudha%E2%80%99s%20life%20was%20good.%20Her%20father%2C%20K%20Narayan%20Iyengar%2C%20was%20the%20director%20of%20Archaeology%20at%20the%20Government%20Museum%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20while%20her%20husband%2C%20R%20B%20Iyengar%2C%20was%20a%20scientist%20and%20close%20associate%20of%20Professor%20C%20N%20R%20Rao.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20lived%20in%20Amsterdam%20where%20he%20researched%20and%20she%20was%20a%20yoga%20trainer.%20But%20when%20Sudha%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20MS%2C%20where%20the%20degenerative%20disorder%20of%20the%20nervous%20system%20would%20soon%20hamper%20her%20movements%2C%20they%20decided%20to%20move%20back%20to%20India%20where%20help%20would%20be%20more%20easily%20available%20for%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20she%20taught%20at%20the%20MES%20Kishore%20Kendra%20in%20Malleswaram%20but%20after%20a%20few%20years%2C%20as%20the%20disease%20progressed%2C%20she%20started%20to%20use%20a%20wheelchair%20and%20soon%2C%20the%20school%20became%20a%20thing%20of%20the%20past.%20A%20friend%20suggested%20she%20create%20a%20play%20area%20within%20the%20house%20compound%2C%20or%20perhaps%20a%20library.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20idea%20soon%20metamorphosed%20into%20a%20summer%20camp%20for%20children.%20Located%20at%20the%20couple%E2%80%99s%20home%20in%20Malleswaram%2C%20which%20was%20thrown%20open%20to%20the%20children%2C%20it%20was%20a%20big%20hit.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGreatly%20inspired%20by%20Sudha%2C%20teachers%20here%20worked%20voluntarily.%20Many%20were%20known%20to%20her%2C%20some%20whose%20chil