2628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EShashi%20Prakash%20Singh%20with%20his%20students.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%20%3Cp%3EHarsh%20Rajput%20came%20to%20Kota%20as%20he%20wants%20to%20get%20into%20an%20IIT.%20He%20is%20one%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98droppers%E2%80%99%2C%20who%20make%20up%20a%20huge%20chunk%20of%20students%20in%20the%20city.%20They%20drop%20a%20year%20out%20of%20college%20to%20just%20focus%20on%20clearing%20the%20entrance%20exam.%20Many%20students%20like%20Harsh%20attempt%20the%20entrance%20exam%2C%20be%20it%20NEET%20or%20JEE%2C%20and%20if%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20clear%2C%20they%20come%20here%20the%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20have%20classes%20for%20even%20longer%20hours%2C%20and%20their%20days%20stretch%20for%2015%20hours%20of%20self-study%20and%20classes%2C%20as%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20board%20exams%20to%20concentrate%20on%20as%20well.%20This%20crushing%20routine%20and%20pressure%20to%20perform%20leads%20to%20a%20lot%20of%20anxiety.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20common%20problems%20Thakur%20and%20his%20team%20hear%20on%20the%20ground%20include%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20unable%20to%20sleep%E2%80%9D%20or%20%E2%80%9CMain%20pareshaan%20hun%E2%80%9D%20(I%E2%80%99m%20worried%20or%20troubled)%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20can%E2%80%99t%20understand%20anything%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20feel%20like%20studying%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20competition%20is%20ruthless%2C%20especially%20in%20NEET%2C%20where%20there%20are%20few%20seats%20in%20government%20medical%20colleges.%20Parents%20tell%20their%20children%20that%20we%20just%20can%E2%80%99t%20afford%20a%20paid%20seat%2C%20adding%20to%20the%20pressure%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Thakur.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDr%20Neena%20Vijayvargiya%2C%20a%20psychiatrist%20in%20Kota%2C%20says%20that%20parents%20need%20to%20support%20their%20children%20and%20understand%20the%20importance%20of%20mental%20health.%20%E2%80%9CBrain%20is%20als